title: Fritz Leiber - Gather, Darkness!
description:
Gather, Darkness! is a science-fiction classic. It tells the story of Armon Jarles, a man on the edge, living amidst the disputes of two rival powers at large in the world. 360 years after a nuclear holocaust ravaged mankind, throwing society back into the dark ages, the world is fraught with chaos and superstition. The new rulers over the masses of humanity are the techno-priests of the Great God, endowed with scientific knowledge lost to the rest of humanity.


Read by Jonathan Davis
Format: MP3
Bitrate: Variable
Unabridged
